snippet.title: The Dokis Hate MC!!!!(DDLC Loser MC MOD)
snippet.description:
It's a very serious and philosophical mod exploring the idea of what if MC was the most despicable of people.And with a chance to enter the Literature Club, he will take any opportunity to be with one of the cute four girls! But, why only one, when you can have more?
Disclaimer: This mod shouldn't be taken seriously, as it's just a comedy mod. Please, before criticizing this mod, I recommend you try it.
